text: Someone argued that making a huge switch case was a good way to make a decompiler, I said why not use a map. Then because Julia taught me to think about instructions I looked at the code for both and it was obvious - use a dang map for syntax but also performance :smile:. Yay Julia for teaching me some comp sci
